| Uncomment the following lines to override default booting behaviour...

| Uncomment this line to generate informational messages for each boot phase as it starts
|SetEval Boot$Verbose 1

| Don't run global PreDesktop scripts
|SetEval BootRun$PreDesk 0

| Don't run STB-specific PreDesktop scripts
|SetEval BootRun$HookPreDesk 0

| Don't boot applications in Resources:$.Apps
|SetEval BootBoot$ResFSApps 0

| Don't boot anything in the !STBBoot.Resources directory
|SetEval BootBoot$Resources 0

| Don't boot anything in the STB-specific Resources directory
|SetEval BootBoot$HookRes 0

| Boot any applications in the non-Pace applications/resources directory
|SetEval BootBoot$Apps 1

| Don't run global Desktop scripts
|SetEval BootRun$Desktop 0

| Don't run STB-specific Desktop scripts
|SetEval BootRun$HookDesk 0

| Run everything in the non-Pace applications/resources directory
|SetEval BootRun$Apps 1

| The maximum size of the CacheFS 'disc' for scrap files (default = 4096K)
|Set CacheFS$Size "2048K"

| The override the default TV type (PAL) to NTSC
|Set TV$Type "NTSC"

| Don't display a splash screen during booting
|SetEval SplashScreen 0

